Headquarters Regions: Greater New York Area, East Coast, Northeastern US
Full Description: Established in 2012 by young visionaries who saw a sea of untapped potential in the education industry, Unipro Education Pvt Ltd is India’s only digital solutions agency that works exclusively with partners in the education sector. In less than four years from its inception, Unipro has worked with over 100 Indian & international clients, providing them targeted digital media solutions that help them reach out to their audiences and improve engagement and conversions. With one of the most promising growth figures in the digital solutions segment, Unipro has grown in excess of 100% YoY in revenues, adding teams at locations including Bangalore, Kolkatta, Indore, Chandigarh, Mumbai, Pune, and the USA  The decision to dedicate its operations to the education industry has a been an astute one for Unipro, considering that 93% of students access the internet daily and 91% use it to search for information about colleges & courses, making the education sector one the most lucrative markets for digital marketing solutions. A full service digital agency and a forerunner in marketing to the education sector, Unipro provides customers with value driven offerings throughout their journey from impressions to enrolments.  Combining an unparalleled understanding of the education sector and rich expertise in digital solutions, Unipro brings to its customers a portfolio of services that leverage the best in digital technology and are tailored to work perfectly in the education industry’s context. Unipro’s service portfolio includes: •	Advertising and Media Solutions o	Search (Google, Yahoo, and Bing) advertisements, Display advertisements, Mobile advertisements, YouTube advertisements, Behavioural Re-targeted display advertisements, and Content Marketing o	Search Engine Optimization  o	Direct Media Buying on Education sites o	E-mailer campaigns, Custom Audience Targeting campaigns, Lookalike Data Targeting campaigns, and Gmail Sponsor Promotions •	Technology Integrated Solutions o	Lead Management System – A unique CRM solution that helps in tracking, managing, and distributing leads in real time o	Content Management System (CMS) for websites o	Behavioural Re-targeting platform that helps brands bring back their potential customers o	Student online application platform that also includes an integrated payment gateway •	Creative solutions o	Website design & development and Un-bounce landing pages o	HTML templates, Rich Media Creatives, Social Media Creatives •	Social Media Management o	Page Management (Facebook, YouTube, LinkedIn, Twitter, GooglePlus) o	Blog & Forum Management o	Online Reputation Management (ORM) o	User Engagement campaigns and Content Marketing strategies. As a pioneer in its field, Unipro has helped advertisers in the education sector usher in a new trend where offline marketing has been traditionally dominant, while fostering long standing partnerships with top notch educational institutions both in India and across the globe. With a deep understanding of how the education industry works, Unipro is currently pushing the envelope with a strong focus on research and developing technology driven digital solutions that make marketing in the education sector a much more streamlined process. For enquiries, please contact media@unipro.co.in

Description: Dognition is a company that utilizes cognition tests to determine a dog's intelligence and personality profile.
Headquarters Regions: Research Triangle, East Coast, Southern US
Full Description: Have you ever wondered what your dog was thinking?  Dognition provides an answer.  More than a dog intelligence test, Dognition helps you see the world through the eyes of your four-legged friend.  Grounded in fifteen years of canine cognition research, Dognition brings to bear what leading scientists have learned about dog intelligence to help owners gain fresh perspective on dog behavior, and most importantly how their own fur-friend thinks.  There's no need to worry about whether or not you have a smart dog; Dognition is not a mere dog IQ test that would tell announce "smart dog" or not.  Instead, Dognition describes your dog's everyday problem solving abilities across five key cognitive areas: memory, reasoning, communication, cunning and empathy.  Dognition's dog games make it fun and easy to gain insight never before available.   Owners can play first two sets of dog games at now cost.  Purchase a Dognition Assessment Toolkit to get all five sets of dog games and your dog's complete Dognition Profile report, detailing his way of seeing the world.  Continue with an annual Dognition membership and receive a new dog game each month that spotlights a new element of your dog's intelligence, plus dog trainer tips and activities that are customized to your dog's cognitive style, as well as special offers from valuable partners such as as KONG and Purina ONE. We believe your business is not earned until after your loan is closed and you are completely satisfied.  Network Capital was recently named as one of the Best Places to Work in Orange County. This fourth annual program was created by the Orange County Business Journal and Best Companies Group. The actual rankings will be published in the Orange County Business Journal’s special report on the Best Places to Work in the October 29, 2012, issue of the Orange County Business Journal*. We are proud to say our employees work hard for you, and they like doing so.  With support from our technology partners Oracle, Redhat, Microsoft, and Cisco we are able to provide our best in class home loan delivery platform to service our clients. Our system matches you with the best home loan for your situation. We are always thinking of ways to make things easy even at closing. Sign your closing documents electronically anywhere in the country. From the airport to your living room it’s that simple.  Although we invest in technology we understand our clients are people and that is why a Network Capital home loan specialist will always be available to answer your questions. Our home loan specialists are among the best in the industry with an average of eight years mortgage banking experience.  With an overall 98% customer satisfaction rate our dedicated home loan specialists will deliver on our promise of high quality service. Pick up the phone, give us a call and let us prove to you that you have made the best choice in a lender.

Headquarters Regions: San Francisco Bay Area, Silicon Valley, West Coast
Full Description: Delta, founded in 1971, is a global leader in power and thermal management solutions. Its mission statement, “To provide innovative, clean and energy-efficient solutions for a better tomorrow,” focuses on addressing key environmental issues such as global climate change. As an energy-saving solutions provider with core competencies in power electronics and automation, Delta's business categories include Power Electronics, Automation, and Infrastructure. Delta offers some of the most energy efficient power products in the industry, including switching power supplies with efficiency over 90%, telecom power with up to 98%, and PV inverters with up to 98.8% efficiency. We have also developed the world’s first server power supply certified as 80 Plus Titanium with over 96% efficiency. We regularly invest 6% to 7% of our annual sales revenues in R&D and have worldwide R&D facilities in Taiwan, China, Europe, India, Japan, Singapore, Thailand, and the U.S. Delta is a frequent recipient of international awards and related recognition for innovation, design, and corporate social responsibility. Since 2011, Delta has been selected each year for the prestigious Dow Jones Sustainability™ World Index (DJSI World). In 2016, we were also included in the DJSI Emerging Markets Index for the 4th consecutive year. Delta was ranked by CDP (formerly the Climate Disclosure Project) at the Climate Change Leadership Level. In response to the challenge of climate change, Delta will remain committed to the research and development of innovative, energy-saving products, solutions and services that contributing substantially to the sustainable development of mankind.
